params._ref: The primary reference that a Registry links to. This can be any type of content and is typically used to reference an index or url.
params._registryToken: The address of the Registry's Token. Registry Tokens are issued upon staking Infinity Token to transfer the ownership of a Registry Entry.
params._registryType: The Registry's Type. Registry Types are defined globally at the Registrar and used to categorize Registries.

params._subdomain: The subdomain to index the Registry entry.
